WEBVTT

00:07.549 --> 00:15.645
But as Kundalini rises, on every center
you start getting the light of that center.

00:15.645 --> 00:20.645
At the first center you get back your innocence,

00:20.940 --> 00:30.196
your eyes become innocent, your behavior becomes
innocent, you are not filled with lust and greed,

00:30.392 --> 00:38.220
you don’t look at things with lust and greed, but
you look at things with innocence, which is a very

00:38.220 --> 00:45.600
big thing that people have lost and that you get
back and such a person develops many qualities.

00:45.600 --> 00:54.480
One of them is that such a person is full of
fragrance, such a person has a tremendous gravity,

00:56.820 --> 01:03.840
tremendous gravity, and such a
person has tremendous dynamism, and

01:04.380 --> 01:09.500
attraction is a bad word so I don’t
want to use it, but magnetical.

01:09.720 --> 01:18.485
His magnets is awakened within him, this
is the center of your magnet of the earth.

01:18.840 --> 01:26.400
Such a person develops a tremendous
sense of roots and sense of direction,

01:26.400 --> 01:29.460
you place him anywhere he will know where to go.

01:29.460 --> 01:35.220
Like birds, you place birds anywhere they
know which side is north, south, east, west.

01:35.220 --> 01:39.633
In the same way you also develop your lost

01:39.780 --> 01:46.802
innocence and your magnet within you
by which you have proper direction;

01:47.100 --> 01:55.203
but the highest of all you develop the proper
direction to wisdom which is the wise thing to do.

01:55.320 --> 02:02.460
You just don't do stupid things, you just
don't do, even if you ever try to do it,

02:02.460 --> 02:08.179
you will not do it, because you know
it is so stupid, just you don’t do it.

02:08.460 --> 02:14.100
I mean it is so simple to
be wise than to be stupid,

02:14.100 --> 02:18.987
because if you have to be stupid you
have to go out of the way to be stupid

02:18.987 --> 02:26.100
and idiotic; but if you want to be normal
and wise is the easiest thing to do.

02:26.191 --> 02:36.180
But what people do is to do things that would make
them more and more stupid, nonsensical, because

02:36.180 --> 02:45.226
also some people told Me they do it, the reason
being they think they have a nuisance value.

02:45.226 --> 02:49.680
Like in London now we have one funny
stuff going on, they call it what?

02:49.680 --> 02:50.400
"Punk rock."

02:50.400 --> 02:52.380
You see, it’s a funny stuff.

02:52.380 --> 02:58.800
Now poor things they don’t know what they
are doing it, and I think the only value

02:58.800 --> 03:09.480
of that punk rock system is this: that
they try to sort of make a nuisance out

03:09.480 --> 03:15.180
of them so that people feel attracted towards
them or sort of a significance out of them.

03:15.180 --> 03:21.903
But when you become a realized soul you realize
your significance, because you understand

03:21.903 --> 03:31.200
you are part and parcel of the whole and that your
significance is to give Realization to others, the

03:31.200 --> 03:38.100
highest of highest, that’s what you have to do now
you are a saint, and that’s how the whole attitude

03:38.100 --> 03:48.065
of cheapiness, of outward shallowness finishes
and you become a serene, dignified personality.

03:48.240 --> 03:54.060
This is not possible through any sermon,
any lecture, it’s only possible when the

03:54.060 --> 04:02.431
Kundalini rises you become like a very
dignified child, very dignified child.

04:02.431 --> 04:12.000
I’ve seen one beautiful painting done
of Mother Mary being taught first time.

04:12.074 --> 04:16.634
You see Her as a child, She is
a very dignified personality,

04:16.740 --> 04:18.856
as a child, She is about ten years of age.

04:18.856 --> 04:25.038
I’ve seen My own grandchildren who are
not very old but extremely dignified.

04:25.140 --> 04:28.380
They walk like kings, behave like kings.

04:28.380 --> 04:33.720
In every behavior you find there’s such a
dignity, they’ll never do something shallow,

04:33.720 --> 04:38.220
they never ask for anything, they never
weep for anything, they never cry for

04:38.220 --> 04:43.500
anything, they are so dignified and they
understand it so well what is dignity is.

04:43.500 --> 04:50.100
I don’t have to tell them, because they are born
realized, in the same way you become that, nobody

04:50.100 --> 04:56.466
has to tell you that "do this, or do that," but
you understand that you must have self-respect.

04:56.580 --> 05:01.980
This happens to you automatically,
this is actualization, nobody has to

05:01.980 --> 05:04.020
tell you that "you be dignified," you just become.

05:04.020 --> 05:09.452
I’ve seen people who were absolutely absurd,
even from this punk rock we got some people

05:09.660 --> 05:13.740
and they were so changed that
people could not recognize them,

05:13.740 --> 05:19.500
but one thing bad has happened with this
punk rock that they put some sort of dye

05:19.500 --> 05:26.160
in their head and since then their eyes became
very weak, because these dyes I think made the

05:26.160 --> 05:33.480
optic globe covered with some sort of a color and
you can’t see properly, and the eyes became very

05:33.480 --> 05:39.600
weak and it took some time for us to remove
the effect of those dyes from their head.

05:39.600 --> 05:46.080
We go headlong, "what’s wrong?" There is nothing
wrong in this world if it is a stupid fool,

05:46.080 --> 05:52.260
but for a wise man there are very many things
which are absolutely wrong, and there are very

05:52.260 --> 05:59.674
many things which are absolutely correct, so
you develop your wisdom by this first center.
